    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly such a great find! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for its next adventure. It runs beautifully and has been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
