      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm selling my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you're headed to work or planning a fun weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road. It's been well-loved and looked after, so you're getting a great ride at a fair price. I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
