      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its high-redline performance and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and corner-exit stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a subframe reinforcement inspection, ensuring the rear multi-link suspension remains structurally sound. The atmospheric induction and rasp of the tuned exhaust provide an authentic analog experience. It is a mechanically robust machine that reflects the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
